{"tid":756293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"七旬老翁港鐵站偷《成報》被捕 (10:28)","createTime":"2018-07-26T02:30:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T05:18:25.000Z","uid":14918,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"d82f4e853697f8d457b5388e4cb4795a629cd395","tid":756293,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T02:30:21.000Z","msg":"港鐵南昌站發生偷竊案。今晨6時許，一名七旬老翁在港鐵南昌站一間尚未營業的便利店外，順手牽羊拿取未曾疊報的《成報》的其中一張報紙。剛將報紙送到便利店的37歲黃姐送報工人見狀阻止，但被老翁的雨傘打中手臂。警方接報到場，將該名76歲徐姓老翁，以盜竊及襲擊拘捕。"},{"pid":"d049f139d74ef864ad09a6253c3aded9520ff888","tid":756293,"uid":28279,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T02:31:41.000Z","msg":"拉佢啱喇，而家班老嘢當自己大鳩哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e26bc78cef949f9a4ad485b2ce42d32d3378bd9","tid":756293,"uid":14918,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T02:32:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180726/s00001/4bc71f94ed5024acee5b1b020f227b69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180726%2Fs00001%2F4bc71f94ed5024acee5b1b020f227b69.jpg&h=5f239822&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"699eca2a0a128fa129e9be4ad62743189eb1a4ee","tid":756293,"uid":196755,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T02:32:09.000Z","msg":"一張報紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9c22565ab669343a2d21cd8428fc8a799e0c53c","tid":756293,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"699eca2a0a128fa129e9be4ad62743189eb1a4ee","tid":756293,"uid":196755,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T02:32:09.000Z","msg":"一張報紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T02:37:34.000Z","msg":"究竟果張係咩黎呢"},{"pid":"18b74f78c4947ec687e0323cb21782695476d26e","tid":756293,"uid":55416,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T02:40:22.000Z","msg":"好偷唔偷偷成報，